    "content": "<p>The area moment of inertia about the y-axis of a linearly tapered section shown in the figure is _____________ m<sup>4</sup> .</p>\n\n<p>(Answer in integer)</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lz3s8qw2/3e6f45ca-9ffa-4a9d-9115-52343aac25e6/fd079020-4be5-11ef-a793-e1425336250e/file-jaoe38c1lz3s8qw3.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lz3s8qw2/3e6f45ca-9ffa-4a9d-9115-52343aac25e6/fd079020-4be5-11ef-a793-e1425336250e/file-jaoe38c1lz3s8qw3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE ME 2023 Strength of Materials - Moment of Inertia Question 1 English\"></p>\n",
